    <string name="you_page_help_a2">Use Privacy &amp; visibility to pause your profile from search. You can resume anytime.</string>
    <string name="you_page_help_q3">How do I change partner preferences?</string>
    <string name="you_page_help_a3">Open Partner preferences from the You tab. Update age range, location, and lifestyle options, then save. In this demo, changes stay on screen until you leave.</string>
